WEBVTT

00:00:17.330 --> 00:00:18.330
Sara-senpai...

00:00:28.760 --> 00:00:29.960
I love you.

00:00:30.150 --> 00:00:31.510
I never gave you an answer,

00:00:34.830 --> 00:00:36.850
and I know it's too late now.

00:00:39.640 --> 00:00:41.000
I'm so sorry for pushing you away,

00:00:42.300 --> 00:00:43.780
even though you cared for me so much.

00:00:48.100 --> 00:00:51.370
I finally understand
how I really feel now.

00:00:53.520 --> 00:00:54.840
I'm sorry for being so selfish...

00:01:02.340 --> 00:01:03.980
Whether it's the Fuu from the other world

00:01:05.820 --> 00:01:07.080
or your fiancée,

00:01:07.710 --> 00:01:09.360
I don't want to lose you to any of them.

00:01:11.810 --> 00:01:13.270
The Sara-senpai standing here...

00:01:15.190 --> 00:01:16.710
isn't the one who belongs to me.

00:01:18.130 --> 00:01:19.130
But...

00:01:21.010 --> 00:01:22.370
please tell him for me.

00:01:26.250 --> 00:01:28.120
You have to tell him this.

00:01:32.820 --> 00:01:34.570
I love Sara-senpai.

00:01:36.200 --> 00:01:37.660
I truly, deeply love him.

00:01:39.790 --> 00:01:40.790
And so...

00:01:43.990 --> 00:01:44.990
goodbye.

00:02:09.670 --> 00:02:11.610
I finally understand how I feel.

00:02:14.900 --> 00:02:15.900
Fuu...

00:02:17.920 --> 00:02:19.560
Whether it's the Fuu from the other world

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:21.380
or your fiancée,

00:02:22.210 --> 00:02:24.110
I don't want to lose you to any of them.

00:02:25.990 --> 00:02:26.990
Fuu!

00:02:28.500 --> 00:02:29.660
Where are you?

00:02:31.840 --> 00:02:32.840
Please,

00:02:33.780 --> 00:02:34.840
talk to me!

00:02:35.540 --> 00:02:37.230
I love Sara-senpai.

00:02:38.090 --> 00:02:39.620
I truly love him.

00:02:53.560 --> 00:02:54.860
It's time to go back.

00:03:07.080 --> 00:03:10.200
Where are you going, Fuu?

00:03:11.990 --> 00:03:13.220
Sara-senpai?

00:03:25.010 --> 00:03:26.680
I...

00:03:28.570 --> 00:03:29.620
I can't live

00:03:30.450 --> 00:03:31.980
without you.

00:03:34.180 --> 00:03:35.180
Really?

00:03:35.970 --> 00:03:37.680
Is it really you, Sara-senpai?

00:03:51.630 --> 00:03:52.630
The paper cup phone...

00:03:53.830 --> 00:03:54.960
remember?

00:04:01.960 --> 00:04:02.960
Tap...

00:04:03.940 --> 00:04:05.040
tap-tap...

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:10.680
A signal from the universe.

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:30.400
"The Boy Next World My Destiny"
(Episode 9)

00:05:11.670 --> 00:05:12.670
Is it true?

00:05:12.830 --> 00:05:13.830
Yeah.

00:05:16.570 --> 00:05:17.570
Really?

00:05:17.930 --> 00:05:18.930
I told you, it's true.

00:05:21.050 --> 00:05:22.150
Me from another world?

00:05:23.380 --> 00:05:24.380
Yeah.

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:26.510
Because he didn't have a scar.

00:05:27.630 --> 00:05:29.480
Everyone said it was memory loss, but...

00:05:32.430 --> 00:05:34.830
Did I do anything to you?

00:05:35.520 --> 00:05:36.520
No, nothing.

00:05:37.030 --> 00:05:38.030
It's just...

00:05:38.260 --> 00:05:40.070
he was a Sara-senpai you didn't know.

00:05:44.730 --> 00:05:45.970
What about you, Sara-senpai?

00:05:46.550 --> 00:05:47.910
Did you see the other Fuu?

00:05:50.740 --> 00:05:51.740
No.

00:05:52.300 --> 00:05:54.360
It was just like a bad dream.

00:05:55.600 --> 00:05:56.600
That's all?

00:05:59.700 --> 00:06:00.700
That's all.

00:06:04.320 --> 00:06:05.320
I'm sorry.

00:06:07.010 --> 00:06:08.170
You didn't do anything wrong.

00:06:10.900 --> 00:06:12.690
I finally get it now.

00:06:13.100 --> 00:06:15.520
The Sara-senpai I love
is the one standing right here.

00:06:17.250 --> 00:06:18.920
If I hadn't pushed you away...

00:06:19.050 --> 00:06:20.700
if I hadn't been so stubborn...

00:06:20.970 --> 00:06:22.640
you wouldn't have gotten hurt.

00:06:23.230 --> 00:06:24.230
And you'd still be...

00:06:29.310 --> 00:06:31.080
I'm the one who should apologize.

00:06:33.530 --> 00:06:34.530
I'm sorry.

00:06:38.280 --> 00:06:39.280
Sara-senpai...

00:06:39.920 --> 00:06:40.920
You did nothing wrong.

00:06:45.330 --> 00:06:46.330
I'm sorry.

00:06:49.920 --> 00:06:51.240
You don't need to apologize.

00:06:53.610 --> 00:06:54.610
More importantly,

00:06:56.640 --> 00:06:57.840
can you promise me one thing?

00:07:06.730 --> 00:07:08.620
I'll promise you anything.

00:07:13.960 --> 00:07:16.750
Don't leave me alone.

00:07:19.340 --> 00:07:20.540
I promise.

00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:22.410
I won't leave you.

00:07:33.530 --> 00:07:35.060
Even if you say you hate me,

00:07:36.840 --> 00:07:38.190
I'm never letting go.

00:08:06.950 --> 00:08:08.510
Well, that's that.

00:08:10.380 --> 00:08:13.070
I guess I can finally
retire as Sara's babysitter.

00:08:23.630 --> 00:08:24.940
What's with you?

00:08:25.890 --> 00:08:27.510
Hey, what's wrong?

00:08:34.890 --> 00:08:36.370
This is a good thing, right?

00:08:36.726 --> 00:08:38.166
He's back to normal.

00:08:39.840 --> 00:08:42.030
Otherwise, there's no way
he'd be that cold to Fuu.

00:08:42.670 --> 00:08:44.219
He's had a crush on him since high school.

00:08:44.220 --> 00:08:46.650
He even lied and said
he was his girlfriend.

00:08:52.120 --> 00:08:55.370
Forget what I just said...

00:08:59.180 --> 00:09:00.180
I already knew.

00:09:00.370 --> 00:09:01.690
Sara-senpai told me before.

00:09:04.020 --> 00:09:05.370
Seriously?

00:09:06.130 --> 00:09:07.830
I only found out recently.

00:09:17.220 --> 00:09:18.220
Senpai...

00:09:20.280 --> 00:09:21.440
I have something to tell you.

00:09:23.630 --> 00:09:24.730
What is it?

00:09:24.890 --> 00:09:25.990
Why the serious face?

00:09:26.780 --> 00:09:27.880
What's up?

00:09:30.780 --> 00:09:31.780
I...

00:09:34.730 --> 00:09:36.020
I can read minds.

00:09:38.450 --> 00:09:40.599
Don't treat me like an idiot.

00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:42.710
I'm not, please believe me.

00:09:44.100 --> 00:09:45.200
Then right now,

00:09:45.420 --> 00:09:47.520
do you know what I'm thinking?

00:09:57.030 --> 00:09:58.030
I don't know...

00:09:58.990 --> 00:10:01.000
You really think I'd believe that?

00:10:01.500 --> 00:10:03.210
Do you think I'm that gullible?

00:10:04.420 --> 00:10:05.520
Stop joking around...

00:10:08.150 --> 00:10:09.480
I like you.

00:10:16.760 --> 00:10:18.200
Ever since I realized how I felt,

00:10:18.890 --> 00:10:20.570
I haven't been able to hear your thoughts.

00:10:22.400 --> 00:10:23.830
But please believe me about this.

00:10:44.150 --> 00:10:45.350
Are you okay?

00:10:45.787 --> 00:10:48.247
We were so worried when
we couldn't reach you.

00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:57.060
Do you really remember this time?

00:10:57.690 --> 00:10:59.310
He's completely back to normal.

00:10:59.610 --> 00:11:00.610
Everything's fine.

00:11:02.150 --> 00:11:03.920
Well, I haven't forgiven you yet.

00:11:04.550 --> 00:11:05.550
And before,

00:11:05.590 --> 00:11:08.050
your fiancée even tried to hit Fuu.

00:11:08.630 --> 00:11:11.190
Fuu, why didn't you tell me about that?

00:11:11.580 --> 00:11:12.820
Because nothing happened.

00:11:13.430 --> 00:11:15.550
The other Sara-senpai saved me.

00:11:19.097 --> 00:11:20.297
Sara-senpai...

00:11:22.050 --> 00:11:24.350
do you love Fuu?

00:11:29.190 --> 00:11:30.290
I do.

00:11:32.150 --> 00:11:33.250
Then,

00:11:33.450 --> 00:11:34.550
from now on,

00:11:34.660 --> 00:11:37.000
you have to protect him.

00:11:39.950 --> 00:11:40.960
I promise.

00:11:43.570 --> 00:11:44.700
You know, we...

00:11:44.850 --> 00:11:46.520
we really love Fuu.

00:11:47.090 --> 00:11:47.830
If you make us angry,

00:11:47.831 --> 00:11:48.990
you'll regret it.

00:11:50.460 --> 00:11:51.460
Don't worry.

00:11:55.780 --> 00:12:00.000
I love Fuu more than anyone.

00:12:06.230 --> 00:12:07.430
Oh, don't get all shy now.

00:12:08.110 --> 00:12:09.110
I'm not shy.

00:12:14.220 --> 00:12:15.620
It'll be bad if we're late today...

00:12:24.830 --> 00:12:25.940
Adachi-kun...

00:12:26.740 --> 00:12:27.840
right?

00:12:29.040 --> 00:12:30.040
Yes.

00:12:31.760 --> 00:12:32.760
Did you need something?

00:12:35.240 --> 00:12:36.240
Yes.

00:12:43.560 --> 00:12:44.560
Thank you.

00:12:48.850 --> 00:12:50.010
I'm counting on you.

00:13:06.240 --> 00:13:07.300
Right now?

00:13:07.380 --> 00:13:09.660
Hey, if you have something to say, sing it!

00:13:09.920 --> 00:13:10.770
Come on, sing it out!

00:13:10.771 --> 00:13:12.330
We've never heard you sing before.

00:13:12.400 --> 00:13:13.600
True, let's go to karaoke...

00:13:18.980 --> 00:13:20.510
Did you have something to say?

00:13:20.930 --> 00:13:21.930
Yeah.

00:13:22.460 --> 00:13:23.820
It's about Sara-senpai.

00:13:23.860 --> 00:13:25.950
- What? Is he cheating on you?
- Huh?

00:13:26.020 --> 00:13:27.020
No!

00:13:27.380 --> 00:13:28.380
Listen...

00:13:30.700 --> 00:13:33.480
He's been acting really strange lately.

00:13:43.250 --> 00:13:44.470
I'll go get it.

00:13:48.790 --> 00:13:50.170
Tea?

00:13:51.060 --> 00:13:52.060
Bread?

00:13:53.030 --> 00:13:54.030
Soda?

00:13:55.650 --> 00:13:56.650
Cake?

00:13:59.440 --> 00:14:00.540
Wrong, wrong, wrong.

00:14:07.430 --> 00:14:08.840
The answer was yogurt.

00:14:13.400 --> 00:14:14.840
Then the next day when I got home...

00:14:23.040 --> 00:14:24.590
See? Isn't that weird?

00:14:27.360 --> 00:14:29.919
You're just bragging
about your relationship.

00:14:29.920 --> 00:14:31.120
Seriously.

00:14:32.070 --> 00:14:34.770
Listen to me, guys! I'm
actually worried here.

00:14:34.950 --> 00:14:35.950
Well...

00:14:36.150 --> 00:14:37.680
why don't you just get back at him?

00:14:38.800 --> 00:14:39.800
Get back at him?

00:14:40.320 --> 00:14:41.420
Yeah, with a surprise.

00:14:41.500 --> 00:14:42.940
That's a great idea!

00:14:43.040 --> 00:14:45.820
Make it something huge and flashy.

00:14:46.655 --> 00:14:49.481
[*sounds of lovey dovey teasing*]

00:14:50.200 --> 00:14:51.200
That's great.

00:14:51.850 --> 00:14:52.850
Yeah.

00:14:55.660 --> 00:14:57.520
Oh, speak of the devil.

00:14:58.850 --> 00:14:59.850
Have a good one.

00:15:01.510 --> 00:15:02.510
Sorry, guys.

00:15:11.950 --> 00:15:13.190
I'll walk you to class.

00:15:14.730 --> 00:15:16.480
Don't you have a class too, Sara-senpai?

00:15:17.070 --> 00:15:18.700
You promised me you wouldn't skip.

00:15:23.570 --> 00:15:24.570
Fine, I get it.

00:15:26.380 --> 00:15:27.580
Call me later.

00:15:28.430 --> 00:15:29.430
Yes, sir.

00:15:30.040 --> 00:15:31.950
I'll be a good boy.

00:15:43.320 --> 00:15:44.320
Bye!

00:15:46.010 --> 00:15:47.010
Good luck.

00:15:52.520 --> 00:15:53.520
Fuu.

00:15:57.760 --> 00:15:59.450
Adachi, do you have class now?

00:16:00.040 --> 00:16:01.370
No, well...

00:16:01.440 --> 00:16:02.920
I need you to come somewhere with me.

00:16:06.000 --> 00:16:07.000
Just come with me.

00:16:09.420 --> 00:16:10.420
What is it?

00:16:10.970 --> 00:16:12.520
Are you in trouble again?

00:16:12.540 --> 00:16:13.540
No.

00:16:13.910 --> 00:16:15.290
Someone wants to see you.

00:16:15.860 --> 00:16:17.300
You'll understand when we get there.

00:16:33.270 --> 00:16:35.060
I don't really want to skip class.

00:16:35.310 --> 00:16:36.310
Will this be quick?

00:16:38.240 --> 00:16:39.680
I finally found you.

00:16:46.560 --> 00:16:47.760
What's going on?

00:16:47.800 --> 00:16:49.670
She asked me for a favor the other day.

00:16:49.720 --> 00:16:50.980
She wanted to clear things up.

00:16:52.150 --> 00:16:53.150
Huh?

00:16:53.420 --> 00:16:55.830
She was forced into that engagement.

00:16:56.710 --> 00:16:58.590
She didn't mean to get in your way.

00:16:59.340 --> 00:17:01.230
So, I was hoping you two could make up.

00:17:03.180 --> 00:17:04.380
You...

00:17:04.900 --> 00:17:07.100
You've been lying to Sara
this whole time, haven't you?

00:17:09.790 --> 00:17:10.890
What are you talking about?

00:17:11.096 --> 00:17:12.196
Don't play dumb.

00:17:13.350 --> 00:17:15.650
You made Sara act like a total stalker.

00:17:16.370 --> 00:17:18.510
I don't know how you did it...

00:17:19.150 --> 00:17:21.170
but Sara's been acting
strange because of you.

00:17:22.040 --> 00:17:23.739
Hey... I thought you were going to make up?

00:17:23.740 --> 00:17:24.850
A long time ago...

00:17:25.620 --> 00:17:28.090
it was decided that Sara would be mine.

00:17:29.960 --> 00:17:31.530
Give my Sara back to me!

00:17:35.140 --> 00:17:36.900
Who Sara-senpai belongs to...

00:17:37.390 --> 00:17:39.090
is for him to decide.

00:17:41.300 --> 00:17:42.500
And besides...

00:17:43.320 --> 00:17:44.399
You tricked my friend.

00:17:44.400 --> 00:17:46.400
Don't you feel any shame?

00:17:47.930 --> 00:17:49.849
That's because you're
the one tricking Sara!

00:17:49.850 --> 00:17:50.850
Stop it!

00:17:52.340 --> 00:17:53.340
Sara...

00:17:56.270 --> 00:17:57.810
The one I love is Fuu.

00:18:01.110 --> 00:18:02.100
Sara, listen to me...

00:18:02.101 --> 00:18:03.720
Don't ever contact us again.

00:18:09.210 --> 00:18:10.210
Are you okay?

00:18:10.790 --> 00:18:11.790
Yeah.

00:18:22.280 --> 00:18:26.210
That was definitely more than just a slap.

00:18:31.580 --> 00:18:32.820
You sewer rat...

00:18:41.680 --> 00:18:42.680
Does it hurt?

00:18:55.670 --> 00:18:56.970
I'm really okay.

00:19:01.300 --> 00:19:02.300
I'm sorry.

00:19:03.580 --> 00:19:04.580
This is all my fault.

00:19:05.830 --> 00:19:07.250
It's not your fault, Sara-senpai.

00:19:18.400 --> 00:19:20.570
But if you ever cheat on
me, that's a different story.

00:19:26.490 --> 00:19:29.850
I would never cheat on you.

00:19:44.430 --> 00:19:47.830
You're the most
important person in my life.

00:20:13.850 --> 00:20:15.050
I told you, didn't I?

00:20:15.540 --> 00:20:16.740
I believe you.

00:20:38.000 --> 00:20:39.000
Good.

00:20:44.400 --> 00:20:49.000
Senpai's birthday...

00:20:58.460 --> 00:21:01.410
His phone number...

00:21:22.410 --> 00:21:23.660
It's my birthday.

00:21:47.650 --> 00:21:48.990
Ta-da!

00:22:10.660 --> 00:22:11.660
Oh...

00:22:14.610 --> 00:22:15.610
honestly...

00:22:33.643 --> 00:22:36.085
(Seiki High School, 27th Graduating Class)

00:22:36.110 --> 00:22:38.387
Is this from the year I graduated?

00:22:54.800 --> 00:22:57.000
(Thank you)

00:22:57.060 --> 00:22:58.260
What is this?

00:23:15.250 --> 00:23:16.250
We...

00:23:17.586 --> 00:23:19.936
we didn't even know
each other back then, right?

00:23:29.100 --> 00:23:31.570
"You made Sara act like a total stalker."

00:23:33.010 --> 00:23:35.050
"I don't know how you did it..."

00:23:35.740 --> 00:23:37.710
"Sara's been acting
strange because of you."

00:23:46.900 --> 00:23:49.900
(I'm sorry. I lied.)

00:23:59.630 --> 00:24:01.479
Don't look so annoyed.

00:24:01.480 --> 00:24:03.530
I'm just here to pick up the homework.

00:24:04.070 --> 00:24:05.590
You could've just gotten it at school.

00:24:06.850 --> 00:24:09.060
Look, I have my reasons.

00:24:21.970 --> 00:24:23.989
I'm glad to see you're happy and all...

00:24:23.990 --> 00:24:25.970
but isn't it about time you told Fuu?

00:24:26.130 --> 00:24:28.169
Tell him you're not actually
from a parallel world.

00:24:28.170 --> 00:24:30.770
That you've actually
liked him since high school.

00:24:31.090 --> 00:24:32.090
Taiga...

00:24:37.420 --> 00:24:38.420
You...

00:24:38.600 --> 00:24:39.800
Have you been inside my house?

00:24:40.800 --> 00:24:41.800
What?

00:24:42.870 --> 00:24:44.070
Why are you asking me that?

00:26:47.550 --> 00:26:50.640
I hope this world can reach a happy ending.

00:26:53.740 --> 00:26:54.840
I truly hope so.